art.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE160\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE160\">DE160</a></td><td>Further evaluation needed</td><td>Additional assessment is necessary before making a recommendation regarding the specified immunization</td></tr></table></div>"
